ZH: 1. 长征是中国共产党的一项重大战略行动。
EN: The Long March was a major strategic action by the Chinese Communist Party.
ZH: 2. 长征是中国革命史上的壮举，标志着中国共产党的崛起。
EN: The Long March was a feat in Chinese revolutionary history, marking the rise of the Chinese Communist Party.
ZH: 3. 长征中的红军战士们经历了艰苦的长途跋涉。
EN: The Red Army soldiers endured arduous long-distance journeys during the Long March.
ZH: 4. 长征是在艰苦条件下进行的，但取得了巨大的历史意义。
EN: Although conducted under harsh conditions, the Long March had tremendous historical significance.
ZH: 5. 长征是中国革命的一次重要转折点。
EN: The Long March was an important turning point in the Chinese Revolution.
ZH: 6. 毛泽东是长征的主要领导人之一。
EN: Mao Zedong was one of the key leaders of the Long March.
ZH: 7. 长征期间，红军士兵们面临许多困难和挑战。
EN: During the Long March, the Red Army soldiers faced many difficulties and challenges.
ZH: 8. 长征成为了中国共产党在人民中威望和号召力的来源。
EN: The Long March became a source of prestige and appeal for the Chinese Communist Party among the people.
ZH: 9. 长征过程中，红军士兵们展现了极强的毅力和团结精神。
EN: During the Long March, the Red Army soldiers showed tremendous perseverance and unity.
ZH: 10. 长征是中国革命史上的一座丰碑，永远值得纪念。
EN: The Long March is a monument in Chinese revolutionary history that will always be worth commemorating.

ZH: 11. 长征的路程总共约有约1万2千公里。
EN: The total distance of the Long March was about 12,000 kilometers.
ZH: 12. 长征期间，红军士兵们经历了艰苦的自然环境和敌人的追击。
EN: During the Long March, Red Army soldiers experienced harsh natural environments and enemy pursuit.
ZH: 13. 长征期间，红军士兵们在艰难的条件下进行了多次战斗。
EN: During the Long March, Red Army soldiers engaged in multiple battles under challenging conditions.
ZH: 14. 长征标志着中国共产党与国民党的斗争进入了新的阶段。
EN: The Long March marked a new phase in the struggle between the Chinese Communist Party and the Kuomintang.
ZH: 15. 长征中的红军士兵们始终保持着顽强的斗志。
EN: The Red Army soldiers during the Long March always maintained a tenacious fighting spirit.
ZH: 16. 长征是中国革命的伟大历程之一。
EN: The Long March is one of the great journeys of the Chinese Revolution.
ZH: 17. 长征是中国共产党历史上的一个重要里程碑。
EN: The Long March is an important milestone in the history of the Chinese Communist Party.
ZH: 18. 长征期间，红军士兵们发扬了无畏的精神。
EN: During the Long March, Red Army soldiers exemplified a spirit of fearlessness.
ZH: 19. 长征是中国革命胜利的一个重要因素。
EN: The Long March was an important factor in the victory of the Chinese Revolution.
ZH: 20. 长征让红军士兵们积累了宝贵的战斗经验。
EN: The Long March allowed Red Army soldiers to accumulate valuable combat experience.
